<inglise> Commission Regulation (EC) No 1478/97 of 28 July 1997 fixing the actual production of olive oil and the unit amount of production aid for the 1995/96 marketing year </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 1478/97, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks oliivi&otilde;li tegelik toodang ja tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta majandusaastaks 1995/96 28. juuli 1997 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 136/66/EEC of 22 September 1966 on the establishment of a common organization of the market in oils and fats (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1581/96 (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. septembri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1581/96, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 of 17 July 1984 laying down general rules on the granting of aid for the production of olive oil and of aid to olive oil producer organizations (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 636/95 (4), and in particular Article 17a (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 17. juuli 1984. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84, milles s&auml;testatakse oliivi&otilde;li tootmise puhul antava abi ja oliivi&otilde;li tootjate organisatsioonidele antava abi &uuml;ldised eeskirjad, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 636/95, (4) eriti selle artikli 17a l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 of Regulation No 136/66/EEC provides that the unit amount of the production aid must be reduced where the actual production for a given marketing year exceeds the maximum guaranteed quantity fixed for that marketing year; whereas, however, producers whose average production is less than 500 kilograms of olive oil per marketing year are not affected by that reduction; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; artiklis 5 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra &uuml;hiku kohta peab v&auml;hendama, kui asjaomase majandusaasta tegelik toodang &uuml;letab k&otilde;nealuse majandusaasta jaoks kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud garanteeritud maksimumkogust; siiski ei m&otilde;juta see v&auml;hendamine tootjaid, kelle keskmine toodang on v&auml;iksem kui 500 kilogrammi oliivi&otilde;li majandusaasta kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 17a of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 provides that, in order to determine the unit amount of the production aid for olive oil which may be paid in advance, the estimated production for the marketing year concerned should be established; whereas, for the 1995/96 marketing year, the estimated production aid which may be paid in advance was fixed by Commission Regulation (EC) No 1888/96 (5); </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 artiklis 17a s&auml;testatakse, et v&otilde;imaluse korral ettemakstava oliivi&otilde;li tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks &uuml;hiku kohta tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealuse majandusaasta t&otilde;en&auml;oline toodang; 1995/96. majandusaasta t&otilde;en&auml;oline toodang ja selle toetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta, mida v&otilde;ib ette maksta, on kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1888/96; (5) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, pursuant to Article 17a (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84, not more than eight months after the end of the marketing year the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the aid has been recognized must be determined; whereas, to that end in accordance with Article 12a of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3061/84 (6), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1110/97 (7), the Member States concerned must notify the Commission, not later than 31 May following each marketing year, of the quantity recognized as qualifying for the aid in each Member State; whereas as a result of those communications the quantity eligible for aid for the 1995/96 marketing year amounts 625 000 tonnes for Italy, 2 450 tonnes for France, 445 000 tonnes for Greece, 375 000 tonnes for Spain and 34 000 tonnes for Portugal; </inglise>
<eesti> vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 artikli 17a l&otilde;ikele 2 tuleb hiljemalt kaheksa kuu jooksul p&auml;rast majandusaasta l&otilde;ppu kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata tegelikult toodetud kogused, mille puhul on tunnustatud abi saamise &otilde;igust; selleks peavad liikmesriigid vastavalt komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 (6) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1110/97 <hi rend="sup"> 7) </hi> artiklile 12a teatama komisjonile hiljemalt j&auml;rgmise majandusaasta 31. maiks k&otilde;nealuses liikmesriigis toetuse saamise tingimustele vastava koguse; k&otilde;nealuse teavitamise kohaselt on toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavad kogused 1995/96. majandusaastal Itaalia puhul 625 000 tonni, Prantsusmaa puhul 2450 tonni, Kreeka puhul 445 000 tonni, Hispaania puhul 375 000 tonni ja Portugali puhul 34 000 tonni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas recognition by the Member States of those quantities as qualifying for the aid implies that the checks referred to in Regulations (EEC) No 2261/84 and (EEC) No 3061/84 have been carried out; whereas, however, fixing actual production in accordance with the information on the quantities recognized as qualifying for Community aid by the Member States does not prejudge the conclusions that may be drawn from verification of the accuracy of that information under the clearance of accounts procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuste koguste tunnustamine liikmesriikide poolt toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavatena eeldab m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 ja m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 osutatud kontrollide l&auml;biviimist; tegeliku toodangu kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramine vastavalt teabele koguste kohta, mida liikmesriigid on tunnustanud &uuml;henduse toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavatena, ei piira j&auml;reldusi, mida v&otilde;idakse teha kontrollides k&otilde;nealuse teabe &otilde;igsust raamatupidamisarvestuse kontrollimise ja heakskiitmise k&auml;igus; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the quantity actually produced, the unit amount of the production aid provided for in point (b) of the fifth subparagraph of Article 5 (1) of Regulation No 136/66/EEC should also be fixed; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas tegelikult toodetud koguseid, tuleks samuti kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 viienda l&otilde;igu punktis b etten&auml;htud tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the exceptional circumstances which have led to a certain delay in fixing actual production for the 1995/96 marketing year and in order to ensure that payment of the balance of the production aid for that marketing year is made under the budget for the 1997 financial year, it is necessary to fix 15 October 1997 as the final date for that payment by derogating from Article 12b (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 3061/84; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas erandlikke asjaolusid, mis on viinud 1995/96. majandusaasta tegeliku toodangu kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise edasil&uuml;kkamiseni, ja selle tagamiseks, et k&otilde;nealuse majandusaasta tootmistoetuse l&otilde;ppmakse tehakse 1997. majandusaasta eelarvest, on vaja erandina m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 artikli 12b l&otilde;ikest 3 k&otilde;nealuse makse tegemise viimaseks kuup&auml;evaks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata 15. oktoober 1997; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the 1995/96 marketing year for olive oil: </inglise>
<eesti> 1995/96. majandusaastal on oliivi&otilde;li puhul: </eesti>
<inglise> - the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the production aid has been recognized and which is eligible for reimbursement by the EAGGF Guarantee Section is 1 481 450 tonnes, </inglise>
<eesti> - tegelikult toodetud kogus, mida on tunnustatud kui tootmistoetuse tingimustele vastavat ja mis vastab Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi tagatisrahastu h&uuml;vitise saamise tingimustele, 1 481 450 tonni, </eesti>
<inglise> - the unit amount of the production aid shall be ECU 129,57 per 100 kilograms. </inglise>
<eesti> - tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta on 129,57 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 kilogrammi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> Notwithstanding Article 12b (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 3061/84, Member States shall pay the balance of the production aid for the 1995/96 marketing year, payable to producers whose average output is not less than 500 kilograms, not later than 15 October 1997. </inglise>
<eesti> Olenemata m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 artikli 12b l&otilde;ikest 3, teevad liikmesriigid tootjatele, kelle keskmine toodang on v&auml;hemalt 500 kilogrammi, 1995/96. majandusaasta tootmistoetuse l&otilde;ppmakse hiljemalt 15. oktoobril 1997. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 28 July 1997. </inglise>
